reviews.review: There was a lot of stuff that confused me in this film, but otherwise, it was pretty good.
They did a great job with the story and wrapped everything up nicely

I wish I could give no stars, the movie was easily the second worst star wars movie ever made, poor writing, massive plot holes, an attempt to suck up to real fans by including some old characters that falls flat because it ruins the characters arcs from the real movies. I felt like I was watching a poorly done reboot of the first trilogy written by someone who wasn't a fan. give this movie a hard pass , even if its free.

It took care of questions raised in the last jedi that came out of the blue, it brought some of the EU lore into canon, and I enjoyed it.   Some may hate it, some may love it, I suggest seeing it for yourself and making an unbiased opinon.
Loved it! Yes it has its issues BUT it was a fun movie! Must see it again!

I thought It was the best of all the Star Wars movies. I don't understand all the negative comments. It wrapped everything up brilliantly, it was exciting, poignant, great action...I honestly  can't think of anything bad to say about it. The haters need to lighten and enjoy a good story. It was a great escape from an awful time in this world of ours.
Somethings were left unanswered but if you can ignore that you have one heck of a blockbuster! lots of emotions running.
Great throwback to the originals, really enjoyed it.

It was a good movie, had a good vision for the ending of the series, but many minor mistakes caused it to just not feel right. These terrible choices added up and just unraveled what was left of the cool scenes or events occurring. Really hard to describe without examples and without spoiling so ill just leave it at that. If you like Star Wars, you will like the movie BUT some things will happen in the movie that will just leave you baffled and confused why they didn't choose to go along this other path that would've created a better story and ending.
Plenty of action, but abrams was definitely trying to clean up the mess of last Jedi . Should have been slit in two movies. Way too much story crammed into 2.5 hours
